room_title: Escape room "Lab Rats" by 15 Locks in Austin
review: We did Lab Rats with a bunch of coworkers and it was exceptionally fun! The staff there is friendly, and the puzzles are interesting and promotes collaboration, which is what we were looking for for a work place team building activity. Highly recommend!!

room_title: Escape room "Lab Rats" by 15 Locks in Austin
review: Did "Lab Rats" with 12 other people and had a great time.  The room is so well designed and encouraged participation from everyone, not just a few dominant people.  The hour goes fast so everyone needs to be on their game.

room_title: Escape room "Lab Rats" by 15 Locks in Austin
review: It was an awesome experience my team had a blast. Fully recommend with 5 stars !

room_title: Escape room "Lab Rats" by 15 Locks in Austin
review: This is a top of the line entertainment service. With perplexing puzzles, friendly service, and a reasonable price I will gladly make multiple trips through the coming years from Fort Worth in order to solve new rooms. The rooms provided are great for a date night or family outing.

room_title: Escape room "Lab Rats" by 15 Locks in Austin
review: This place was awesome! Staff was great, puzzles required teamwork, and the locks were physically unique. Can't say enough about how great of an experience this was. Will be back for more!
